#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:5
# 16feda1f96034ae1bd8587e12c30bb67
msgid "Battle the Horde!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:7
# 81962054ebf2487f9c264c85fdc0a742
msgid "You have come far, hero, but the next step on your Hero's Path is the deadliest yet. You will face the Horde, an onslaught of savage and fierce Minotaurs, an unyielding tide of destruction."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:10
# 7e6d100ba6fc4519be8dfd2c470e05be
msgid "As the battle progresses, more and more Minotaurs will join the ranks of the Horde. They will attack at every opportunitym but a strong defense can turn their aggression against them. The Horde will bring idols, talismans, and other remnants of previous conquests. On the battlefield, these artifacts will inspire the Horde to frenzy, speeding up the assault. But if you can send those artifacts to the graveyard, you'll reap the rewards. The Horde's sorceries make its creatures difficult to handle in combat, but these sorceries can backfire at times."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:17
# ea963300067348f0b1ee595041bdbd5d
msgid "Can you defeat the Horde? To battle!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:20
# cb5f7cd879ca4ab9b8065f7323832c02
msgid "**The \"Battle the Horde\" Challenge uses the Regular Magic rules, with the following exceptions:**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:23
# 87144765d13c40b3a10a513a004bbf87
msgid "Special Rules for the Player"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:25
# d9eaa42ae58f4acab5edcff27ed43b46
msgid "You start with up to three different Hero cards on the battlefield. (You don't need a Hero to play.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:26
# bade42dba0aa44da832e5f4e3aa2c75b
msgid "**You take three turns at the start of the game, before the Horde takes its first turn.**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:27
# acdb254cdc324ad5baec5468233881b7
msgid "You can attack the Horde with your creatures as thought it were a player, even before the Horde takes a turn."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:28
# 921c1dde717544df8881aa77a2f97079
msgid "The Horde doesn't have a life total, but its library serves a similar purpose. **If the Horde would lose life, put that many cards from the top of its library into its graveyard.** Watch for artifact cards in the Horde's library. They each have a \"hero's reward\" ability that triggers when the artifact card is put into the graveyard."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:32
# 4509ab1523cc461dbce0dfbe9a7190d2
msgid "You can target the Horde with spells and abilities a thought it were a player, even before the Horde takes a turn."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:36
# 8f267192a313493ca2c742c2307dbb06
msgid "Special Rules for the Horde"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:38
# 943a7d4b1faf4082bf989970564054b0
msgid "At the beginning of the Horde's precombat main phase each turn, reveal the top two cards of the Horde's library. Then the Horde casts those cards. (The Horde's artifacts each cause an additional card to be revealed and cast, starting the turn after the artifact enters the battlefield.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:41
# fd5ee959d31c4cdda7a60c14aed93186
msgid "You make the choice if the Horde needs to make a decision."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:42
# da27ec05cb274561b35d7544e7be1cf0
msgid "Ignore effects that would cause Horde to draw or discard cards, or perform any impossible actions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:43
# 88acafbc42494d098002e680ad5aaf3b
msgid "If on of the Horde's permanents would move to any zone other than its library or graveyard, that card is put into the Horde's graveyard."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:47
# 0c555150fbd1459fbca4ef58bb5aeec3
msgid "Winning the Challenge"
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:49
# 9406e2b178fe413fb3573590c98f6207
msgid "You win the game if the Horde has no cards left in its library and the Horde controls no creatures on the battlefield."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:51
# 3cbea248381d483fab234da7ef2dce3d
msgid "You lose the game if you have 0 or less life or if you have to draw a card and your library is empty."
msgstr ""

#: ../../BNG_horde.rst:53
# 09d6eabe36984c929fe7e963b8c5f62f
msgid "For a more difficult challenge, try taking only two turns before the Horde's first turn. For an easier challenge, take four turns."
msgstr ""

